@c ----------------------------------------------------------------------
@node fdim, math
@findex fdim
@subheading Syntax

@example
#include <math.h>

double fdim(double x, double y);
@end example

@subheading Description

@code{fdim} computes the "positive difference", that is:

* @math{@var{x} - @var{y}} if @math{@var{x} > @var{y}}
* else +0.0

@subheading Return Value

@code{fdim} returns the greater of @math{@var{x} - @var{y}} or +0.0.

@subheading Portability

@portability ansi, posix
